{"tid":2308481,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果有機會攬住佢訓","createTime":"2020-12-02T02:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T05:13:39.000Z","uid":354869,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d015c9c8259bc55fc8a044a9c40b7a39c9f616a4","tid":2308481,"uid":354869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T02:23:11.000Z","msg":"早排同另一半去開房，終於係生日留到佢過夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以為每晚可以揸佢軟綿綿嘅波波訓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點知佢勁醒訓 我轉個身佢都醒，之後佢話就算以後同居都唔想同人訓<br />\n<br />\n但佢之前同ex過夜都係屈係張單人床，連續成個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解輪到我就唔得，又話驚我係咁嘈醒佢，佢會好炆<br />\n<br />\n如果真係好中意對方，你哋會唔會介意對方嘈醒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2d3a6a2b2d16b23ad7292b116a4e30227b0b32","tid":2308481,"uid":74927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"帽事既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06f0a3b6be15a0de1ef4c331a68187eee3b522d","tid":2308481,"uid":340631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T02:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ed739a79441222313cc2444e0a8215d6d55099","tid":2308481,"uid":173973,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T02:25:22.000Z","msg":"成日手多訓訓下渣人對波 比我都唔同你訓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de41b79de2a2cb12f79aa2bdeafe2efd9209f3a3","tid":2308481,"uid":385103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T02:40:06.000Z","msg":"會介意，但唔會話唔一齊訓"},{"pid":"fac8efb36f717a80f427d0c2a8dac4966f5ec9fc","tid":2308481,"uid":313630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:27:22.000Z","msg":"有啲明 我同朋友/男朋友瞓都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />